--- !u!114 &1403956206
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1403956205}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ffc6c9685281c2644b0260f7fd7c31ad, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueBox: {fileID: 65148739}
  linePrefab: {fileID: 6200175676582406942, guid: b57ba745fe2c87d419773a43c4bdfaa7, type: 3}
  dialogueAdvanceButton: {fileID: 71453708}
  characters:
  - characterName: Silque
    textColor: {r: 0.7433963, g: 0.09958705, b: 0.09958705, a: 1}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 1842357824}
    characterAnimator: {fileID: 1842357826}
  - characterName: Knight
    textColor: {r: 0.11980766, g: 0.76281685, b: 0.8037735, a: 1}
    characterSprite: {fileID: 751662354}
    characterAnimator: {fileID: 751662356}
  dialogueLines:
  - text: Oh thank the gods you are still alive my princess
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: Huh who are you.
    characterIndex: 0
  - text: I am a knight of your kingdom and I have come to rescue you
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: Oh thank you sir knight. The last thing I remember is being attacked and
      then I awoke here
    characterIndex: 0
  - text: 'Yes our kingdom was attacked by the demon lord and their were few survivors. '
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: I even believe your own family to be dead princess
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: I see, I am not shocked of this but I wonder why keep me alive?
    characterIndex: 0
  - text: It was most likely to prevent knights like myself from fighting back but
      now you are free
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: Will you be coming with me Sir Knight?
    characterIndex: 0
  - text: Unfortunately no. I am greatly wounded. I used what little life I had left
      to get here
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: So you are dying then. I shall honor your sacrifice to save me. But does
      this mean that I am the one who will have to defeat the demon lord
    characterIndex: 0
  - text: Unfortunately yes. You are the only one left who can princess but do not
      worry
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: In my escape from the castle I managed to get the Tome of Change
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: With this even one like yourself with little combat experience can be a
      great warrior
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: All I must do is offer up my soul in exchange for you to unlock its great
      power
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: Now with this magic I shall release you from your dark bindings and you
      can take this tome and save the world from the demon king
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: Thank you Sir Knight I will never forget you
    characterIndex: 0
  - text: Also one last thing. Your Controls
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: Move left and right with left and right arrows
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: Attack with Z and when your gauge is full press x to use the book
    characterIndex: 1
  - text: Press X and any direction button once the book has been used to do a special
      attack
    characterIndex: 1
  charDelay: 0.02
  moveUpSpeed: 250
  advanceKey: 97
